---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageNav from "../components/PageNav.astro";
---

<Layout title="Sobredeterminación de la Cultura: Automatización y Ocio">
  <main class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-12 lg:py-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Left Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="space-y-4 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0s; opacity: 0;">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">Ficha Técnica 042</span>
          <h1 class="font-body text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-extrabold text-primary leading-tight tracking-tight">
            Automatización <br/>& Ocio
          </h1>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md">
            Análisis de la sobredeterminación cultural bajo el ciclo sistémico de la automatización productiva y la expansión del tiempo creativo.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-[2rem] border-l-4 border-primary animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s; opacity: 0;">
          <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-primary mb-2">Hipótesis Central</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant italic">
            "La automatización no desplaza al humano, sino que transmuta el esfuerzo físico en capacidad de ocio creativo, alimentando el retorno cultural."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Cards -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-8 relative mt-35">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 relative z-10">
          <!-- Card 1: Automatización -->
          <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-[2rem] animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s; opacity: 0;">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary-container">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">precision_manufacturing</span>
              </div>
              <h2 class="font-body font-bold text-2xl text-primary">Automatización</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-6">Infraestructura tecnológica y procesos de optimización que absorben la carga operativa sistémica.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">cycle</span>
              Sustentabilidad Técnica
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2: Cultura -->
          <div class="glass-card p-1 rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden group animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s; opacity: 0;">
            <div class="relative h-56 md:h-64 w-full rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden">
              <img alt="Expresión Cultural" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" src="/images/sobredeterminacion/cultura.png" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/80 to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6">
                <h2 class="font-body font-bold text-2xl text-on-primary">Cultura</h2>
                <p class="text-on-primary-container text-xs font-medium">Manifestación de la Identidad Social</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 3: Ocio y Tiempo (Full Width) -->
          <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10 shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/15 relative overflow-hidden animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s; opacity: 0;">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-10">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-7xl md:text-9xl">palette</span>
            </div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-secondary-container">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">theater_comedy</span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="font-body font-bold text-2xl text-secondary">Ocio y Tiempo</h2>
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="p-4 md:p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low border-b-4 border-secondary">
                  <h4 class="font-body font-bold text-secondary mb-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Tiempo Libre</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-3">Liberado por la Robotización masiva de tareas.</p>
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary/40">smart_toy</span>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 md:p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low border-b-4 border-secondary">
                  <h4 class="font-body font-bold text-secondary mb-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Creatividad</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-3">Capacidad de innovación estética y conceptual.</p>
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary/40">auto_awesome</span>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 md:p-6 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low border-b-4 border-secondary">
                  <h4 class="font-body font-bold text-secondary mb-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Recreación</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-3">Descanso reparador y equilibrio biopsicosocial.</p>
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary/40">bedtime</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Section -->
    <section class="mt-20 bg-tertiary-container text-on-tertiary-container rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-12 relative overflow-hidden group animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s; opacity: 0;">
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-1/3 bg-gradient-to-l from-white/5 to-transparent"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 md:gap-12">
        <div class="max-w-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed">analytics</span>
            <h3 class="font-body text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Tasa de Retorno Cultural</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-on-tertiary-container/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Índice que mide el impacto de la eficiencia tecnológica sobre la producción de bienes inmateriales. El reciclaje entre la automatización y la cultura genera un ecosistema de crecimiento infinito.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <div class="px-6 py-4 bg-white/10 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10">
              <span class="block text-2xl font-black text-white">84.2%</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-fixed font-bold">Eficiencia Social</span>
            </div>
            <div class="px-6 py-4 bg-white/10 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10">
              <span class="block text-2xl font-black text-white">+12.5</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-fixed font-bold">Variación Ocio</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="shrink-0 shadow-amber-50 shadow-xs p-6 md:p-8 rounded-full border border-white/10 text-center">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-4 block text-primary-fixed">eco</span>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">Nota de Sistema</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium italic opacity-80">"Reciclaje entre la automatización <br/>y la cultura"</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="mt-16 md:mt-20 pt-8 border-t border-outline-variant/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-outline animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s; opacity: 0;">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm font-medium">
        <span>© 2024 Sobredeterminación Sistémica</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-outline-variant rounded-full"></span>
        <span>Análisis de Productividad Social</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-8 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex-wrap justify-center">
        <span class="text-primary cursor-help">Eco-Ecosistema</span>
        <span class="text-secondary cursor-help">Riqueza Inmaterial</span>
        <span class="text-tertiary cursor-help">Sociedad Líquida</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <PageNav
    prev={{ href: "/genialidad", label: "Genialidad", sublabel: "Innovación" }}
    next={{ href: "/reciclaje-residual", label: "Reciclaje", sublabel: "Residual" }}
  />
</Layout>